Package com.visionreport.core.models

Class ReportModel

java.lang.Object
com.visionreport.core.models.ReportModel
public final class ReportModel extends Object
Represents the internal data model for an entire Vision Report.

Aggregates system information, test cases, statistics, and chart data, and serves as the primary data source for FreeMarker template rendering. Populated by ReportGenerator from API-level VisionReport data.

Includes metadata such as report title, generation date and time, and summary statistics (pass/fail/skip counts). Can also hold ChartData for visual analytics.
